      <rules>
        <rule id="91cd-ebc7-b892-3f86" name="Fieldcraft" hidden="false">
          <description>Kroot gain +1 to their Cover Save in woods or jungles. Kroot in woods or jungles do not have to roll a Difficult Terrain test; they can always move up to 6&quot;. In addition, they can see and shoot through 12&quot; of woods or jungle terrain rather than the 6&quot; that would normally be the case.</description>
        </rule>
