          <rules>
            <rule id="a060-438c-6a80-3795" name="Skilled Flyers" hidden="false">
              <description>Vespids are skilled at negotiating dangerous obstacles whilst fighting to full effect. They may re-roll failed Dangerous Terrain tests.</description>
            </rule>
            <rule id="33d7-9c85-d0b8-a2f6" name="Fleet of Wing" hidden="false">
              <description>The Stingwings are surprisingly agile for their size, and many warriors have paid the prioce for underestimating their speed. They are Fleet, as described in the Warhammer 40,000 Universal Special Rules.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
